550
00:23:16,399 --> 00:23:17,399
Bag is stapled.

551
00:23:17,434 --> 00:23:19,301
You grab it, walk away,
don't look in the bag.

552
00:23:20,865 --> 00:23:22,138
I suppose I have, Your Honor.

