00:23:44,861 --> 00:23:46,239
Answer the question, Agent Manello.

566
00:23:46,263 --> 00:23:47,796
Objection.

567
00:23:48,660 --> 00:23:50,199
Yes or no.

568
00:23:50,233 --> 00:23:51,248
Objection.

569
00:23:51,283 --> 00:23:53,481
