730
00:31:20,528 --> 00:31:21,862
I don't want that job.

731
00:31:21,896 --> 00:31:23,296
You're so judgmental.

732
00:31:23,331 --> 00:31:24,664
Is that supposed to be an insult?

733
00:31:24,699 --> 00:31:26,600
- I can do better.
